OL,6,FBut he was given an eight year
OL,7,Fsentence due to chat messages on the
OL,8,Fsocial media platform, Telegram, and
OL,9,Fhe was also wrongly identified in a
OL,10,Fvideo.
OL,12,FIn court the prosecution argued that
OL,13,Fit was proof he was part of a gang,
OL,14,Fbut three Appeal Court judges have
OL,15,Fruled his conviction was unsafe, and
OL,16,Fhe's been freed after serving three
OL,17,Fyears in jail.
