OL,6,FAt the trial the court heard that
OL,7,Fafter Ade's best friend John Soyoye
OL,8,Fwas murdered in Moston in 2020 revenge
OL,9,Fattacks were discussed in postings on
OL,10,FTelegram, and Ade sent messages
OL,11,Fincluding the postcode of someone he
OL,12,Fbelieved was responsible.
OL,14,FSpeaking from prison he said he
OL,15,Fregretted what he said in the chat,
OL,16,Fadding that John wouldn't have wanted
OL,17,Fanyone to take revenge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
