OL,6,FBut the prosecution argued Ade was
OL,7,Fpart of the M40 gang, they used
OL,8,Fcomments from the group chat, a
OL,9,Fpicture of him with money to his ear
OL,10,Fand a 9 second video of a teenager
OL,11,Frapping in a blue bandana with gang
OL,12,Fcolours as proof of gang membership.
OL,14,FAde consistently denied that it was
OL,15,Fhim in the video, and said that it was
OL,16,Fa boy called Tyrone.
OL,18,FLast December Tyrone Numa came forward
OL,19,Ffor an appeal hearing and gave
OL,20,Fevidence to confirm it was him in the
OL,21,Fvideo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
