OL,6,FHis evidence led to the quashing of
OL,7,FAde's conviction.
OL,9,FThe court said "The video clip was
OL,10,Frelied on to show that Ade was closer
OL,11,Fto the M40 gang than he accepted and
OL,12,Fwas part of the chain of evidence
OL,13,Flinking Ade to the gang."
OL,15,FNow legal experts are raising concerns
OL,16,Fthat the laws used to convict Ade are
OL,17,Funreliable.
