OL,6,FDr Patrick Williams explains, "Where
OL,7,Fan individual may have committed and
OL,8,Foffence, joint enterprise allows for
OL,9,Fall individuals to be potentially
OL,10,Fconvicted".
OL,12,FKeir Monteith KC says "Conspiracy is a
OL,13,Flittle bit different, people,
OL,14,Fcertainly within my profession would
OL,15,Fsee it as easier to prove than joint
OL,16,Fenterprise."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
