OL,6,FHe adds that there is a place for the
OL,7,Flaws in the legal system if they are
OL,8,Fapplied correctly, but Dr. Williams
OL,9,Ffeels that there is something
OL,10,Fproblematic about the way that Greater
OL,11,FManchester Police use them.
OL,13,FHe says "We have a police force who
OL,14,Fare just simply coming out of special
OL,15,Fmeasures.
OL,17,F"We have a police force therefore that
OL,18,Fisn't very good at preventing violent
OL,19,Fcrime.
