OL,6,F"What they've become really adept at
OL,7,Fis using legal doctrines like joint
OL,8,Fenterprise and conspiracy to almost
OL,9,Fdemonstrate that they are being
OL,10,Feffective at responding to the
OL,11,Fproblems of crime and criminality."
OL,13,FIn a statement Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice said: "We understand there have
OL,15,Fbeen concerns in some communities
OL,16,Faround joint enterprise cases, which
OL,17,Fis why we produced a comprehensive
OL,18,Freport in 2023 commissioned by, and
OL,19,Fpresented to, the Mayor of Greater
OL,20,FManchester.
