OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,7,Fsaid: "The majority of the convictions
OL,8,Fwere upheld.
OL,10,F"However, based on fresh evidence not
OL,11,Favailable at the time of the trial,
OL,12,FAdemola Adedeji's conviction alone has
OL,13,Ftoday been quashed by the Court of
OL,14,FAppeal.
OL,16,F"The Court did not order a re-trial.
OL,17,FWe respect the decision of the Court."
